{"tid":2402973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"央視春晚 | 陳偉霆為大會打頭陣  成龍將與張韶涵合唱《明天會更好》","createTime":"2021-02-10T20:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T07:49:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3b489bc51e93196f7485c93074380ed8819f0dac","tid":2402973,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T20:59:37.000Z","msg":"內地央視每年舉辦的經典度歲節目《春晚》節目名單昨晚（10/2）正式出爐，今年同樣有不少大明星出場表演，其中陳偉霆、佟麗婭、歐陽娜娜將打頭陣開場；劉德華將與其他藝人一齊表演《牛起來》；甄子丹為武術表演；成龍將與張韶涵合唱《明天會更好》；近年在內地大熱、正懷孕約7個月的胡杏兒將表演小品《開往春天的幸福》；周杰倫、迪麗熱巴、奚夢瑤等均會亮相表演。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210210/436303720993525760670839.jpeg/k6YiPBMPyF0-p2VCIzqOMbVQktd6fht31Cl639Qpet8?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210210%2F436303720993525760670839.jpeg%2Fk6YiPBMPyF0-p2VCIzqOMbVQktd6fht31Cl639Qpet8%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=0a76aad2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e990889566daa97502ff8f9e79aad5b9b37013e","tid":2402973,"uid":383914,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T21:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32519a95e9494007cca05b59888405cb13f7a3a","tid":2402973,"uid":126226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"出現張韶涵 就會諗范瑋琪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d38821389c4a946818ca59b4cc1771bde547d8","tid":2402973,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"春晚同歡樂今宵無咩分別 得低文化水平同窮人先鍾意睇"},{"pid":"671e03a6762661e7f304e44c7093c8fc1f9865a6","tid":2402973,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32519a95e9494007cca05b59888405cb13f7a3a","tid":2402973,"uid":126226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"出現張韶涵 就會諗范瑋琪 <img src=\"/ass